    "id": "a1-de-het",
    "title": "de vs het",
    "level": "A1",
    "explanation": "Most Dutch nouns use de. Some common nouns use het. Learn the article together with the noun: de tafel, het huis.",
    "examples": [
      {
        "dutch": "de tafel",
        "english": "the table"
      },
      {
        "dutch": "het huis",
        "english": "the house"
      }
    ],
